* Iron Raptor closes in on the CF after walking for a bit with Prowl in her 
arms, nodding before and watching Fliq scurry off towards the cr chambers a 
while ago.
But she stops once Prowl lifts his weight from her shoulders, reluctantly 
letting go of him as he receives a transmission from Epyon.
She missed how close they use to be and feeling his against her, even though 
he had been weak, had made her feel good. Just to be close like that.
< Any time. >
She continues quietly towards the CF doors, leaving Prowl to take care of 
whatever business he had with Epyon before she received the thoughts from 
Prowl just before reaching the doors.
So, two members of his crew were missing, and he was starting to make plans 
to dismantle his ship. It must be for that idea that Prowl had before after 
the first battle that they got back from.
